Package Model.Base

Class TurboEngine

java.lang.Object
Model.Base.Engine
Model.Base.TurboEngine
public class TurboEngine extends Engine
TurboEngine represents one of the types of engines the cars can use. This type uses a Turbo which is used when calculating the speedfactor. The speedfactor is used to calcualate how much the speed will increase. The turbo is either on or off. When its on the speedfactor is slightly larger which makes the engine slightly stronger.
